title: 10 Takeaways from Week 3
itunes:title: 10 Takeaways from Week 3
description:
After a frenetic, thrilling Week 3 of NFL action, DJ and Bucky announce their biggest takeaways from the weekend, including – the Rams’ offense is dynamite (1:00), Patrick Mahomes and the Chiefs’ offense are not a one trick pony (3:10), does Tyrod Taylor make sense for the 49ers (8:30), Josh Allen is Cam Newton 2.0 (13:45), AP still has juice (19:00) & finally, the Cards STARTED THE KID (22:10)!
